org.antlr.v4.tool

Class ToolMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.tool.ANTLRMessage
      • org.antlr.v4.tool.ToolMessage

  • public class ToolMessage
extends ANTLRMessage
    A generic message from the tool such as "file not found" type errors; there is no reason to create a special object for each error unlike the grammar errors, which may be rather complex. Sometimes you need to pass in a filename or something to say it is "bad". Allow a generic object to be passed in and the string template can deal with just printing it or pulling a property out of it.
